606
00:26:56,000 --> 00:26:58,000
especially since the minimum,

607
00:26:58,000 --> 00:27:02,000
is stuck out here away from the origin.

608
00:27:02,000 --> 00:27:05,000
The coordinates phi real and phi imaginary

609
00:27:05,000 --> 00:27:07,000
are not obviously the best

610
00:27:07,000 --> 00:27:09,000
