619
00:27:24,000 --> 00:27:28,000
Now this potential energy doesn't depend on alpha at all.

620
00:27:28,000 --> 00:27:32,000
But it does depend on rho.

621
00:27:32,000 --> 00:27:37,000
It depends on rho in a way which is minimized

622
00:27:37,000 --> 00:27:40,000
when rho is equal to f.

623
00:27:40,000 --> 00:27:42,500
And in fact it takes a good deal

624
00:27:42,500 --> 00:27:45,000
