627
00:27:56,000 --> 00:28:00,000
plus a bit of fluctuation.

628
00:28:00,000 --> 00:28:02,500
In other words, the minimum energy

629
00:28:02,500 --> 00:28:05,000
is when rho is stuck at f.

630
00:28:05,000 --> 00:28:08,000
Anywhere along here, rho is stuck at f.

631
00:28:08,000 --> 00:28:10,000
But you can displace it a little bit,

632
00:28:10,000 --> 00:28:13,000
and let's represent that displacement away from f

633
00:28:13,000 --> 00:28:15,000
by a letter of the alphabet.

634
00:28:15,000 --> 00:28:17,000
And I'm going to choose

635
00:28:17,000 --> 00:28:19,000
the next letter of the

636
00:28:19,000 --> 00:28:21,000
alphabet after f, which is h.

637
00:28:24,000 --> 00:28:25,000
H for what?

638
00:28:25,000 --> 00:28:27,000
H for Higgs.

639
00:28:27,000 --> 00:28:28,000
Okay?

640
00:28:28,000 --> 00:28:30,000
H for Higgs.

641
00:28:30,000 --> 00:28:31,000
All right.

642
00:28:31,000 --> 00:28:34,500
So the Higgs field is just

643
00:28:34,500 --> 00:28:38,000
a displacement of the radial direction

644
00:28:38,000 --> 00:28:39,500
or the radial part of

645
00:28:39,500 --> 00:28:41,000
the field away from its equilibrium.

646
00:28:41,000 --> 00:28:42,000
All right.

647
00:28:42,000 --> 00:28:44,000
Now, it costs a good deal

648
00:28:44,000 --> 00:28:46,000
of energy to excite this Higgs field.

649
00:28:46,000 --> 00:28:47,000
Why?

650
00:28:47,000 --> 00:28:49,000
Because it's got a potential, and

651
00:28:49,000 --> 00:28:51,000
that potential might be rather sharp.

652
00:28:51,000 --> 00:28:53,000
In fact, it is rather sharp.

653
00:28:53,000 --> 00:28:54,000
So,

654
00:28:55,000 --> 00:28:57,000
to some approximation,

655
00:28:57,000 --> 00:28:59,000
some rather good approximation,

656
00:28:59,000 --> 00:29:00,000
we might say

657
00:29:00,000 --> 00:29:03,000
that the low energy behavior

658
00:29:03,000 --> 00:29:09,000
is as if rho were frozen at value f.

659
00:29:09,000 --> 00:29:12,000
Now, this is a very common thing in physics

660
00:29:12,000 --> 00:29:13,000
to say

661
00:29:13,000 --> 00:29:17,000
that there are low energy excitations,

662
00:29:17,000 --> 00:29:19,000
low energy oscillations of a system,

663
00:29:19,000 --> 00:29:21,000
low frequency oscillations,

664
00:29:21,000 --> 00:29:23,000
and high frequency oscillations,

665
00:29:23,000 --> 00:29:25,000
and ignore the fact that,

666
00:29:25,000 --> 00:29:28,000
if we were to ignore the high frequency oscillations,

