00:30:17,500 --> 00:30:19,000
to make a bit of H,

690
00:30:19,000 --> 00:30:21,000
we can just approximately say

691
00:30:21,000 --> 00:30:23,000
that rho is equal to f,

692
00:30:23,000 --> 00:30:26,000
and we find that for the low energies,

693
00:30:26,000 --> 00:30:30,000
for the small energy excitations,

694
00:30:30,000 --> 00:30:34,000
that the Lagrangian is just f squared, a number,

695
00:30:34,000 --> 00:30:39,000
times the derivative of alpha squared.

696
00:30:41,000 --> 00:30:44,000
There is no potential energy associated with alpha.

