00:30:44,000 --> 00:30:46,000
Why is there no potential energy associated with alpha?

698
00:30:46,000 --> 00:30:48,000
For the obvious reason

699
00:30:48,000 --> 00:30:50,000
that we don't gain any potential energy

700
00:30:50,000 --> 00:30:52,000
when we go around the angular direction.

701
00:30:52,000 --> 00:30:53,000
All right?

702
00:30:53,000 --> 00:30:54,000
We, uh,

703
00:30:54,000 --> 00:30:56,000
this is a little bit less familiar

704
00:30:56,000 --> 00:30:58,000
because it has this f in it,

705
00:30:58,000 --> 00:31:00,000
but we could redefine the field.

