00:31:00,000 --> 00:31:02,000
We could redefine the field by inventing a new field.

707
00:31:02,000 --> 00:31:04,000
Call it beta.

708
00:31:04,000 --> 00:31:07,000
Beta is equal to f times alpha.

709
00:31:07,000 --> 00:31:10,000
It's just a rescaling of the field.

710
00:31:10,000 --> 00:31:11,000
All right?

711
00:31:11,000 --> 00:31:13,000
Just a redefinition.

712
00:31:13,000 --> 00:31:14,000
And then,

