00:31:14,000 --> 00:31:17,000
we would rewrite this as just d alpha,

714
00:31:17,000 --> 00:31:19,000
sorry, d beta squared.

715
00:31:22,000 --> 00:31:24,000
No mass term.

716
00:31:24,000 --> 00:31:27,000
No mass term because it doesn't cost any energy

717
00:31:27,000 --> 00:31:30,000
