718
00:31:30,000 --> 00:31:31,000
All right?

719
00:31:31,000 --> 00:31:32,000
No mass term,

720
00:31:32,000 --> 00:31:34,000
and so alpha or beta,

721
00:31:34,000 --> 00:31:36,000
depending on which you want to write,

722
00:31:36,000 --> 00:31:38,000
