723
00:31:38,000 --> 00:31:40,000
It is the Goldstone boson.

724
00:31:40,000 --> 00:31:42,000
And as I said,

725
00:31:42,000 --> 00:31:44,000
what its energy corresponds to

726
00:31:44,000 --> 00:31:47,000
