00:31:56,000 --> 00:31:58,000
from the derivative terms here,

733
00:31:58,000 --> 00:31:59,000
but no potential energy.

734
00:31:59,000 --> 00:32:01,000
So that's the hallmark of a massless particle,

735
00:32:01,000 --> 00:32:04,000
and it's the Goldstone boson.

736
00:32:04,000 --> 00:32:06,000
Goldstone bosons

737
00:32:06,000 --> 00:32:08,000
are the massless particles

738
00:32:08,000 --> 00:32:10,000
